were arrested, he said.
</P>
<P>
Early Monday morning, Customs officers of the Air Cargo
Division found about 400 pirated video compact discs in a parcel
imported from Singapore during a routine cargo examination at the
Air Cargo Examination Hall.
</P>
<P>
