<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, January 7 (Xinhua) -- Pakistan's Supreme Court
decided today to take up next week the petition filed by the
deposed prime minister Benazir Bhutto against the dismissal of her
government by President Farooq Leghari, Chief Justice Sajjad Ali
Shah said.
</P>
