<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Fashion Week Set for Late January </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, January 7 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong Fashion Week will go
into full swing later this month to unveil the latest fall/winter
'97/98 fashion and accessories from over 800 local and overseas
exhibitors, the organizers announced here today.
</P>
<P>
