Beijing University, the Beijing Teachers University, Qinghua
University, Wuhan University, the East China Teachers University
and Fudan University.
</P>
<P>
Among the applicants, 20 people intend for doctor's degree.
</P>
<P>
The applicants will have to pass the entrance exam on April 5
and 6 before being enrolled in September by universities in
China's inland areas.
</P>
<P>
The number of applicants have kept on rise over the past
several years, dozens were recruited last year.  
</P>
