meeting, the ASEANTA noted that it would establish booths in Kuala
Lumpur as part of a "private sector salute to ASEAN's
anniversary."
</P>
<P>
The meeting supported the concept that the anniversary is an
opportunity to promote inbound travel through an ASEAN fare, the
sources said.
