the possibility that Lebanon and Syria will achieve peace with
Israel in 1997.
</P>
<P>
JERUSALEM -- Israel and Palestine Monday decided to ask
international observers to station in Hebron following partial
Israeli troop withdrawal from the West Bank city. 
