<HEADLINE> Fire Accidents Rise in Romania </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, January 6 (Xinhua) -- There have been 269 fire
accidents in Romania since late December, the Fire Control Bureau
reported today.
</P>
<P>
